-- Rubenstein Sees More Private Equity Investments by Sovereign Wealth Funds
-- B y   A r i f   S h a r i f
-- 2010-10-19T07:22:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-19/rubenstein-sees-more-private-equity-investments-by-sovereign-wealth-funds.html
David Rubenstein, co-founder of the
Carlyle Group, said sovereign wealth funds may make more private
equity investments and may do the transactions themselves.
Rubenstein was speaking in Abu Dhabi today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
